  "grammar": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Grammar Spot",
      "content": "• Past of 'to be': I was, You were, He/She/It was, We were, They were\n• was/were born: I was born in 1990.\n• Questions: When were you born? When was he born?\n• Negatives: He wasn't a painter. They weren't French.\n• Irregular verbs: go-went, see-saw, buy-bought, take-took, say-said"
    },
    "ja": {
      "title": "文法のポイント",
      "content": "• 'to be'の過去形: I was, You were, He/She/It was, We were, They were\n• was/were born: 私は1990年に生まれました。\n• 疑問文: When were you born?（いつ生まれましたか？） When was he born?（彼はいつ生まれましたか？）\n• 否定文: He wasn't a painter.（彼は画家ではありませんでした。） They weren't French.（彼らはフランス人ではありませんでした。）\n• 不規則動詞: go-went, see-saw, buy-bought, take-took, say-said"
    },
    "fr": {
      "title": "Point de Grammaire",
      "content": "• Passé de 'to be': I was, You were, He/She/It was, We were, They were\n• was/were born: Je suis né en 1990.\n• Questions: When were you born? (Quand es-tu né ?) When was he born? (Quand est-il né ?)\n• Négations: He wasn't a painter. (Il n'était pas peintre.) They weren't French. (Ils n'étaient pas français.)\n• Verbes irréguliers: go-went, see-saw, buy-bought, take-took, say-said"
    },
    "ko": {
      "title": "문법 포인트",
